msgctxt "@message"
msgid "<b>Adding more profiles</b><br>Just open the folder and place your WAV files there. You can find hundreds of these files in the <a href=\"https://airtable.com/appayGNkn3nSuXkaz/shruimhjdSakUPg2m/tbloLjoZKWJDnLtTc\">HRTF Database<a/>."
